sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant SB as Spring Boot
    participant FS as Firestore
    participant ST as Stripe

    B->>SB: GET /my-account
    SB->>SB: Session auth check
    SB->>FS: Fetch agreements
    FS-->>SB: Agreement data
    SB-->>B: Rendered HTML

    Note over B,ST: Payment Flow

    B->>SB: POST /finance/make-a-payment
    SB->>ST: Create PaymentIntent
    ST-->>SB: client_secret
    SB-->>B: Stripe Elements form
    B->>ST: Confirm payment
    ST->>SB: Webhook event
    SB->>FS: Record payment
